  <revision rev="5" vrev="1">
    <srcmd5>7ab4216dc27946d5310442d6ad1ff943</srcmd5>
    <version>22.1.7</version>
    <time>1781610346</time>
    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>- Update to version 22.1.7.
  * This release contains bug-fixes for the LLVM 22.1.0 release.
    This release is API and ABI compatible with 22.1.0.
- Migrate away from update-alternatives. The packages only provide
  versioned binaries and man pages now. The metapackage wil
  provide symbolic links to the current distro default version.</comment>
